overview: A woman and five men A film made in 1997, tells the story of "Ghazal" Vivi Abdo is a poor and illiterate woman and then becomes the owner of the largest garment factories in Egypt, a powerless and evil woman, her husband Hassan Hosni and her daughter Hanan Turk, That her last husband raped her daughter and killed him.
title: إمرأه وخمسة رجال
